title: Macro's videos of anti-censorship demonstration in Finlan
description:
Six video clips from the demonstration against Internet censorship in Finland on 2008-03-04. As downloaded from: http://macro.divinefilms.fi/miekkari/

Note: the videos are large and perhaps too good in quality, so you might want to download smaller files if available.

The Linux command file describes the files like this:

RIFF (little-endian) data, AVI, 320 x 240, >30 fps, video: Motion JPEG, audio: uncompressed PCM (stereo, 44100 Hz)
